  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993170/extras/d7cb0765fce7810f06b1d4a1b7bb575c.poster.avif?t=1546833622\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993170/extras/d7cb0765fce7810f06b1d4a1b7bb575c.webm?t=1546833622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993170/extras/d7cb0765fce7810f06b1d4a1b7bb575c.mp4?t=1546833622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>THE DEVIL HAUNTS ME</strong> is a survival game about gathering resources, discovering secrets, and avoiding the horror that lurks deep within the woods.<br><br>Cut down trees, hunt deer, and gather water. You need all three of these resources to survive each day. Explore as you wish, and discover secrets in the woods which just might help you survive. But be careful, there's something <i>else</i> in these woods...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993170/extras/e4b619ea58c35b293402cfa08940f4e4.poster.avif?t=1546833622\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993170/extras/e4b619ea58c35b293402cfa08940f4e4.webm?t=1546833622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/993170/extras/e4b619ea58c35b293402cfa08940f4e4.mp4?t=1546833622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
